Descriptive statistics

5mhC expression in bladder cancer

In this section we will describe the dataset, including patients clinical features, preoperative and surgical data, pathologic features of the tumor, as well as preoperative and posoperative treatment, and patients outcome. For this section we will use the full dataset (N = 55). This dataset include all cases that were used for building the tissue microarrays. Data for this section were obtain from medical charts and pathology reports.
